{"language": "html", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>모두의 AX — 커뮤니케이션 패키지</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0f0f10;
  --bg2: #17171a;
  --bg3: #1e1e23;
  --surface: #24242b;
  --surface2: #2c2c35;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
  --text: #e8e6e0;
  --text2: #9e9c96;
  --text3: #5e5c58;
  --accent: #c8f060;
  --accent2: #a8d040;
  --blue: #5b9cf6;
  --blue-dim: rgba(91,156,246,0.15);
  --teal: #3dd6a3;
  --teal-dim: rgba(61,214,163,0.13);
  --purple: #a78bfa;
  --purple-dim: rgba(167,139,250,0.13);
  --amber: #fbbf24;
  --amber-dim: rgba(251,191,36,0.13);
  --red: #f87171;
  --font-display: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  --font-body: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --radius: 10px;
  --radius-lg: 16px;
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* NAV */
.nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(15,15,16,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
  padding: 0 32px;
  height: 52px;
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  margin-right: 32px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  overflow-x: auto;
  scrollbar-width: none;
}
.nav-links::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.nav-link {
  padding: 0 14px;
  height: 52px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  cursor: pointer;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  white-space: nowrap;
  transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-link:hover { color: var(--text); }
.nav-link.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  padding: 80px 48px 64px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -60px; right: -60px;
  width: 400px; height: 400px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,240,96,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 58px);
  line-height: 1.15;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.hero-meta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.meta-pill {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
}
.meta-pill .dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
}

/* MAIN LAYOUT */
.main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px 80px; }

/* SECTION */
.section {
  padding: 64px 0 48px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.section-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.section-num {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-top: 6px;
  min-width: 28px;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.section-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  margin-top: 6px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* CARDS */
.card-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
}
.card-grid-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
.card-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
.card-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }

.card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 24px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
.card-accent { border-left: 3px solid; }
.card-accent.blue { border-left-color: var(--blue); }
.card-accent.teal { border-left-color: var(--teal); }
.card-accent.purple { border-left-color: var(--purple); }
.card-accent.amber { border-left-color: var(--amber); }
.card-accent.accent { border-left-color: var(--accent); }

.card-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.card-label.blue { color: var(--blue); }
.card-label.teal { color: var(--teal); }
.card-label.purple { color: var(--purple); }
.card-label.amber { color: var(--amber); }
.card-label.accent { color: var(--accent); }
.card-label.red { color: var(--red); }

.card-title {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.card-body {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.75;
}
.card-body li {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 3px 0;
  padding-left: 14px;
  position: relative;
}
.card-body li::before {
  content: '·';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--text3);
}

/* PYRAMID */
.pyramid-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; align-items: center; margin: 32px 0; }
.pyramid-level {
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 16px 24px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
}
.pyramid-level:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }
.pyramid-level .lv-badge {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-right: 14px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.pyramid-level .lv-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; flex: 1; }
.pyramid-level .lv-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); text-align: right; max-width: 260px; }

.lv4 { background: var(--purple-dim); border-color: rgba(167,139,250,0.25); width: 55%; }
.lv4 .lv-badge { background: rgba(167,139,250,0.2); color: var(--purple); }
.lv3 { background: var(--blue-dim); border-color: rgba(91,156,246,0.2); width: 70%; }
.lv3 .lv-badge { background: rgba(91,156,246,0.2); color: var(--blue); }
.lv2 { background: var(--teal-dim); border-color: rgba(61,214,163,0.2); width: 85%; }
.lv2 .lv-badge { background: rgba(61,214,163,0.2); color: var(--teal); }
.lv1 { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: var(--border2); width: 100%; }
.lv1 .lv-badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: var(--text2); }

/* TIMELINE */
.timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 28px; }
.timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 7px; top: 8px; bottom: 8px;
  width: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--teal), var(--blue), var(--purple));
  opacity: 0.4;
}
.tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.tl-dot {
  position: absolute;
  left: -24px;
  top: 5px;
  width: 14px; height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid;
  background: var(--bg);
}
.tl-dot.accent { border-color: var(--accent); }
.tl-dot.teal { border-color: var(--teal); }
.tl-dot.blue { border-color: var(--blue); }
.tl-dot.purple { border-color: var(--purple); }
.tl-when {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.tl-head { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.tl-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.75; }

/* TABS */
.tab-bar {
  display: flex;
  gap: 4px;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.tab-btn {
  padding: 8px 18px;
  border-radius: 7px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text2);
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.18s, color 0.18s;
}
.tab-btn.active {
  background: var(--surface2);
  color: var(--text);
}
.tab-panel { display: none; }
.tab-panel.active { display: block; }

/* MESSAGE BOX */
.msg-box {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 28px 32px;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--text);
  white-space: pre-line;
}
.msg-box .highlight { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
.msg-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

/* CERT TABLE */
.cert-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
.cert-table th {
  background: var(--surface);
  color: var(--text2);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  padding: 10px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
}
.cert-table th:first-child { border-radius: 8px 0 0 0; }
.cert-table th:last-child { border-radius: 0 8px 0 0; }
.cert-table td {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text2);
  vertical-align: top;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.cert-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.cert-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
.cert-table .td-main { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.badge-teal { background: var(--teal-dim); color: var(--teal); }
.badge-blue { background: var(--blue-dim); color: var(--blue); }
.badge-purple { background: var(--purple-dim); color: var(--purple); }
.badge-amber { background: var(--amber-dim); color: var(--amber); }

/* CHECKLIST */
.checklist { list-style: none; }
.checklist li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
}
.checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.check-box {
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 4px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.checklist li strong { color: var(--text); }

/* FAQ */
.faq-item {
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.faq-q {
  padding: 16px 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  background: var(--surface);
  user-select: none;
}
.faq-q::after { content: '+'; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text3); transition: transform 0.2s; }
.faq-item.open .faq-q::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
.faq-a {
  display: none;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.8;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.faq-item.open .faq-a { display: block; }

/* INSIGHT BOX */
.insight {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200,240,96,0.06), rgba(61,214,163,0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,240,96,0.15);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 24px 28px;
  margin: 24px 0;
}
.insight-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.insight-text {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.8;
}

/* COPY BTN */
.copy-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  background: var(--surface2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  color: var(--text2);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  float: right;
  margin-top: -4px;
}
.copy-btn:hover { background: var(--accent); color: #000; border-color: var(--accent); }

/* CONVERSION TABLE */
.conv-wrap {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.conv-header {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 48px 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 16px 24px;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 0.07em;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
}
.conv-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 48px 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 14px 24px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 13px;
}
.conv-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.conv-from { color: var(--text2); }
.conv-arrow { text-align: center; color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px; }
.conv-to { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.conv-note { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 3px; }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .card-grid-2, .card-grid-3, .card-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero { padding: 48px 24px 40px; }
  .main { padding: 0 20px 60px; }
  .nav { padding: 0 20px; }
  .lv4 { width: 70%; }
  .lv3 { width: 82%; }
  .lv2 { width: 92%; }
  .pyramid-level .lv-desc { display: none; }
}

/* SCROLL ANIMATION */
.fade-up {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}
.fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">AX COMM KIT</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a class="nav-link active" href="#overview">제도 개요</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#strategy">소통 전략</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#timeline">타임라인</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#messages">메시지 키트</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#cert">인증 상세</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#conversion">DX→AX 전환</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="#checklist">액션 체크</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div style="max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding: 0 16px;">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">LG PRI · HRD 커뮤니케이션 패키지 · 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">'모두의 <em>AX</em>'<br>역량인증 소통 전략</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">AI 기술 발전에 맞춰 Domain DX 역량 체계를 AI 활용 중심의 AX 역량 체계로 전환합니다. 전 구성원의 업무에 생성형 AI를 활용하여 일하는 방식을 바꾸는 전 사 전환 프로그램입니다.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="meta-pill"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>인증 개시: 2026년 4월</div>
      <div class="meta-pill"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--teal)"></div>대상: 전 구성원</div>
      <div class="meta-pill"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--blue)"></div>레벨: Starter → Expert 4단계</div>
      <div class="meta-pill"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--purple)"></div>신청: AXplorer 플랫폼</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main">

<!-- ====== SECTION 1: 제도 개요 ====== -->
<section class="section fade-up" id="overview">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">01</div>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">제도 개요 — '모두의 AX'란 무엇인가</div>
      <div class="section-desc">기존 Domain DX 역량 체계를 AI 활용 중심의 AX 역량 체계로 전환하는 전사 프로그램</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DX vs AX 비교 -->
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-2" style="margin-bottom:32px">
    <div class="card card-accent" style="border-left-color:var(--text3)">
      <div class="card-label" style="color:var(--text3)">AS-IS · DX 역량 체계</div>
      <div class="card-title">Domain DX 역량</div>
      <ul class="card-body">
        <li>목표: 데이터 분석 전문가 육성</li>
        <li>핵심역량: 데이터 분석 기술 학습</li>
        <li>평가방식: 오프라인 과제 / 이론 평가</li>
        <li>참여 대상: DX 전문가 중심 소수</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card card-accent accent">
      <div class="card-label accent">TO-BE · AX 역량 체계</div>
      <div class="card-title">모두의 AX 역량</div>
      <ul class="card-body">
        <li>목표: 전사 AI 활용 통한 생산성 향상</li>
        <li>핵심역량: AI 활용 방식 개선</li>
        <li>평가방식: 교육 이수 + 과제 실적 중심</li>
        <li>참여 대상: 전 구성원 확대</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AX 역량 정의 -->
  <div class="insight">
    <div class="insight-label">AX 역량의 정의</div>
    <div class="insight-text">생성형 AI를 이해하며 업무 AX 관점에서 분석하여, 최적의 AI 솔루션을 활용하여 <strong>업무 생산성을 30% 이상 향상</strong>시킬 수 있는 역량</div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4개 변화 축 -->
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-3" style="margin-bottom:32px">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-label accent">개인 측면의 변화</div>
      <ul class="card-body">
